cord, to provide a new perspective on Nguyen Vietnam from the 1820s to the 1860s.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aAnti-CatholicismzVietnamxHistoryy19th century. 0aMissions, FrenchzVietnamxHistoryy19th century. 0aPersecutionzVietnamxHistoryy19th century. 4aHistory -- Asian. 4aHistory -- European. 7aHISTORY / Asia / Southeast Asia.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804779548zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804779548423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804779548/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles